rows.label: qev093207_MSG0010
rows.name:
Uhh... You can find all the topping ingredients
that we'd need in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093207_MSG0020
rows.name:
You've got fragrant shinuyuni garlic
around Aaroy Plain...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093207_MSG0030
rows.name:
Crisp will peppers are found up at the
northern coast...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093207_MSG0040
rows.name:
And you can see fresh dobobora broccoli
growing at the Floating Reef.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093207_MSG0050
rows.name:
None of those places are even remotely
safe for an ordinary guy like me, so...
It'd be amazing if you could spare the help.[ST:wait ]
